  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN DISCORD</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/5fcbe1023aa45346ed3a7b4c30c15c26.poster.avif?t=1757945603\" width=580 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/5fcbe1023aa45346ed3a7b4c30c15c26.webm?t=1757945603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/5fcbe1023aa45346ed3a7b4c30c15c26.mp4?t=1757945603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Time Is Honey is a cozy idle game where you collect and care for over 150+ types of bees. Each bee has a unique look and boosts your honey production and profits. Unlock and customize hives, then upgrade to complete your bee collection, including special golden bees.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/5615d38e0b480066e130f4c66b1d66dd.avif?t=1757945603\" width=630 height=118 /></span>Discover over <strong>150+ unique bees</strong>, each with its own adorable appearance and stats that increase your profits!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/13f98925e988068fd66336794b4db830.poster.avif?t=1757945603\" width=630 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/13f98925e988068fd66336794b4db830.webm?t=1757945603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/a4cd2b27d10bf3e47f3e168b3283e493.avif?t=1757945603\" width=630 height=118 /></span>Nurture and <strong>feed your bees</strong> with love and care. <strong>Watch your hive grow bigger and bigger</strong> and enjoy the honey they produce as your reward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/798eaeee11c08295711d367aeaaad869.poster.avif?t=1757945603\" width=630 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/798eaeee11c08295711d367aeaaad869.webm?t=1757945603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/798eaeee11c08295711d367aeaaad869.mp4?t=1757945603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/4c0e7e04e0b490351b3b704b83912c9a.avif?t=1757945603\" width=630 height=118 /></span>Open accessory packs to <strong>collect accessories</strong> which you can use to <strong>customize and personalize your bees to your liking.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/0f5807dd0757762454ea3cf999ee869e.poster.avif?t=1757945603\" width=630 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/0f5807dd0757762454ea3cf999ee869e.webm?t=1757945603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/0f5807dd0757762454ea3cf999ee869e.mp4?t=1757945603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/c0ab791c8576c60694922f84407ee3c2.avif?t=1757945603\" width=630 height=118 /></span>Customize your hive by choosing colors for the ground and hive, and adding stickers, making your hive truly <strong>one-of-a-kind.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/80293596fb7819fdfe5133c565a1ce3b.poster.avif?t=1757945603\" width=630 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/80293596fb7819fdfe5133c565a1ce3b.webm?t=1757945603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/80293596fb7819fdfe5133c565a1ce3b.mp4?t=1757945603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/ac8f825935d26d74518397b7866514df.avif?t=1757945603\" width=630 height=118 /></span><strong>Thank you so much for supporting my first game on Steam! As a solo developer, your interest means the world to me. I truly appreciate everyone who tries out the game and/or adds it to their wishlist.</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Time Is Honey is a cozy idle game where you collect and care for over 150+ types of bees. Each bee has a unique look and boosts your honey production and profits. Unlock and customize hives, then upgrade to complete your bee collection, including special golden bees.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/5615d38e0b480066e130f4c66b1d66dd.avif?t=1757945603\" width=630 height=118 /></span>Discover over <strong>150+ unique bees</strong>, each with its own adorable appearance and stats that increase your profits!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/13f98925e988068fd66336794b4db830.poster.avif?t=1757945603\" width=630 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/13f98925e988068fd66336794b4db830.webm?t=1757945603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/a4cd2b27d10bf3e47f3e168b3283e493.avif?t=1757945603\" width=630 height=118 /></span>Nurture and <strong>feed your bees</strong> with love and care. <strong>Watch your hive grow bigger and bigger</strong> and enjoy the honey they produce as your reward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140570/extras/798eaeee11c08295711d367aeaaad869.poster.avif?t=1757945603\" width=630 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic